assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果過左好多年對方搵返你，<br />\n你仲會唔會考慮/嘗試同佢一齊？</blockquote><br />\n點樣隔左好耐突然搵返人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfb status 我 share 左一段野<br />\n佢無啦啦係下面 comment<br />\n見我有反應就即刻 inbox <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果剩係得佢電話呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4f6a1c561d11f592e0f976264975d181a33b41","tid":369854,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:18:21.000Z","msg":"連續2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f83d8c7404d96aff0391c42eda73a88609d4a88","tid":369854,"uid":105436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n明明知道兩個都中意對方<br />\n但最後因爲佢前度翻左黎求復合 而佢心軟揀左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9557628dc0f1242762892190cd1d544a4be2497e","tid":369854,"uid":63648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:19:56.000Z","msg":"宜家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae47daa942678610a4f88f34ca35297f2f0ea60","tid":369854,"uid":104074,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"小六個時同個女仔互相鍾意<br />\n但係我份人太被動 升左唔同中學之後就冇然後了<br />\n依家佢都應該大學畢業 希望你生活幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ed2f6ddff56ff3d37d1b2b1c387a1c65daeb96","tid":369854,"uid":123631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T16:58:41.000Z","msg":"喺外國玩交流團識咗個日本妹，日子耐咗互有感情，個團完結前我寫咗張紙表白，叫佢返到日本先睇，內容大概講我中意佢，但奈何longD冇乜可能，佢覆返我佢都係咁諗，覺得有啲可惜。<br />\n<br />\n利申：而家幾乎冇再聯絡"},{"pid":"9ecdddb783b8d672d5816a8bb42ed7ea69e23b1d","tid":369854,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果過左好多年對方搵返你，<br />\n你仲會唔會考慮/嘗試同佢一齊？</blockquote><br />\n有，大家都結左婚"},{"pid":"db19c657824d5f80c11774ace5cf274787f1f38d","tid":369854,"uid":131962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果過左好多年對方搵返你，<br />\n你仲會唔會考慮/嘗試同佢一齊？</blockquote><br />\n有，大家都結左婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁好容易出事喎⋯"},{"pid":"9324e34dee60875a176ee9995d5d88fb43e306cc","tid":369854,"uid":130140,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:11:12.000Z","msg":"我對佢有好感嗰陣，佢當我係朋友，到幾年後，佢問我會唔會試下同佢一齊，但我已經當左佢係好好好好嘅朋友，剩係想像比佢拖住，我都好有亂倫嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以最後都係做返朋友"},{"pid":"0ab1fb306d0d07eb07918db1f2a7a9a849fb0d64","tid":369854,"uid":139093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:17:41.000Z","msg":"過幾年咩都唔記得啦"},{"pid":"06676c0feea8321f25465dc03913f4698440feb0","tid":369854,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"無以情侶姿態一齊 但做左sp"},{"pid":"e4cf43da71b57b05b727850b89932d7df3931bd4","tid":369854,"uid":2786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:35:51.000Z","msg":"大家都比人hurt完無勇氣一齊<br />\n但明明互相鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩年幾後先知 不過已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c0457aaae30177f8a441a0e4be0d03d650381a","tid":369854,"uid":126947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:42:13.000Z","msg":"佢對我有感覺時我拍緊拖<br />\n到我散左開始對佢有好感時<br />\n佢同左另一個女仔一齊<br />\n後來大家都單身成日一齊行街食飯睇戲<br />\n最後都係無疾而終<br />\n<br />\n永遠記得係hall熄哂燈同你飲住酒睇戲<br />\n差個少少就錫左落去個一秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050eb4fc5453593f847d4b75cb7985fee8095d4f","tid":369854,"uid":73921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:43:05.000Z","msg":"有，一早已經知大家有feel<br />\n我記得佢仲扮哂野問考完試先表白好唔好呢<br />\n我等佢<br />\n一路等<br />\nFeel到唔對路開始冷淡<br />\n有挽回過<br />\n佢話 我地已經變左質 唔係大話但時間真係沖淡左一切<br />\n我好無奈，只可以接受<br />\n點解你過黎拎走我個心玩兩玩就掉落地？<br />\n接近我既係你，走得最快亦係你<br />\n點解自己咁難中意一個人，遍遍就中意左你<br />\n你真係hurt到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為你我以後都唔敢再俾自己放成個心出去。<br />\n2015年既12月係我最懷念又最想忘記既一個月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依加你都已經有女朋友，祝你幸福。"},{"pid":"84c63844c15f2052649b54b9917c2e63bd0c4814","tid":369854,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"依家既結局係妳已經做左兩個孩子的媽媽<br />\n<br />\n當年如果我勇敢一點點,妳會跟我走嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217f903f777c8486e08088c4aea729074fb41ea2","tid":369854,"uid":87437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人有同樣經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果過左好多年對方搵返你，<br />\n你仲會唔會考慮/嘗試同佢一齊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n那些年?"},{"pid":"a876816751ef998da2c1a4454a1140745882309b","tid":369854,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:49:04.000Z","msg":"往事只能回味<br />\n<br />\n向前望吧"},{"pid":"4395c293c057a8139c7586e7b6be911d22c7ff96","tid":369854,"uid":18977,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"你含柒啦 我用咗兩年先放低你 <br />\n你試下再搵翻我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我一定飛咗而家呢個同你一齊</span><br />\n唔好搵翻我呀仆街"},{"pid":"53338bf344a06588537faaca550b4aaa63f82d7e","tid":369854,"uid":37941,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你含柒啦 我用咗兩年先放低你 <br />\n你試下再搵翻我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我一定飛咗而家呢個同你一齊</span><br />\n唔好搵翻我呀仆街</blockquote><br />\n我鄧你條女慘<br />\n水抱"},{"pid":"6a649b7d3e23cc8ba6