"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T20:16:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係衰心軟 驚應承佢會hurt到另一個男仔 再加上覺得自己襯唔起佢 糾結冇耐就直接兩邊都拒絕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知自己個心搖擺不定 寧願封閉自己 心痛都係自己痛 都唔想纏住人唔放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝福佢地搵到個比我好嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我好掛住你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea6178608bcb974a7acd5ce2bfd270005632bd39","tid":369854,"uid":100260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T20:34:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有<br />\n明明知道兩個都中意對方<br />\n但最後因爲佢前度翻左黎求復合 而佢心軟揀左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我情況一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d91144d8b856c566851a32989b024dbe3587ca","tid":369854,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T21:35:53.000Z","msg":"搵人做水泡嘅真係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b43b07aa8643fd570f152dae9431cc15644c11","tid":369854,"uid":98624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:37:39.000Z","msg":"有，中四個時大家鍾意大家，但因為個時係大毒撚，好怕羞<br />\n三年後同佢示愛話無feel"},{"pid":"65be4c18f0b9289e50a64fe2d4ff2a814a0bb5ad","tid":369854,"uid":61336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T22:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有，中四個時大家鍾意大家，但因為個時係大毒撚，好怕羞<br />\n三年後同佢示愛話無feel</blockquote><br />\n人地根本無鐘意過你，唔好ff啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ca002094bdb6cd5a266767ee12461328e1f9c9","tid":369854,"uid":125006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T23:47:56.000Z","msg":"要點先放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad374ac057eb9d8d0d6490870ee50bdac3c86ab2","tid":369854,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T23:53:55.000Z","msg":"唉，而家就面對緊！但我自卑，覺得配佢唔起，結左婚養唔掂人，所以都係無行埋！唯有日夜守護住佢，佢有問題就幫佢解決啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"773e9a99fbf8d36db38c2dde6e56a808f486b7f8","tid":369854,"uid":98624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有，中四個時大家鍾意大家，但因為個時係大毒撚，好怕羞<br />\n三年後同佢示愛話無feel</blockquote><br />\n人地根本無鐘意過你，唔好ff啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nok"},{"pid":"0f21bbc44bb38c07b3a5e7e08b54caa0cafdd9cf","tid":369854,"uid":71548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"無用架，一齊左又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相愛都唔可以解決一切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d88dc31bc0e903e45e31fd8cb86d863d65cd27","tid":369854,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:11:36.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n係我鍾意佢先，但當初佢冇興趣<br />\n後尾佢都後料<br />\n個一段時間大家都有feel<br />\n但我on9feel唔到<br />\n冇一齊到"},{"pid":"4dfb308a1cb754ed4f4f2d358199130c30776b5a","tid":369854,"uid":139345,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:22:52.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n小六個陣同個女仔互相都知道對對方有feel<br />\n佢都有主動寫信俾我，希望升中之後都可以keep住聯絡<br />\n但我知道衰on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  怕俾屋企人發現無回信俾佢，更加無開始到段關係，f3個陣想搵返佢，但佢已經有男朋友了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfe2d7e03b8bcbd8306d44a602196481f7914579","tid":369854,"uid":135885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n當時DSE大家有共同目標一齊溫書<br />\n佢俾曬暗示我 但因為我可能DSE後過外國讀驚要long d 所以我成日扮唔知 想keep到放榜先落決定<br />\n最終當然係愈嚟愈淡 想挽回已經太遲<br />\n而家佢都有男朋友 我就仲係自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過點都好 我一定會永遠記住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=